{"ts":"2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z","author":"codex-root","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"## Reproduction\n\nRun the non-dry release pipeline on a clean checkout with release-relevant commits after the last tag. version.mjs applies the daily candidate before release:verify, so a test literal tied to the previous release fails despite package.json and src/cli.ts matching.\n\n## GitHub evidence\n\nIssue #65 and Actions run 29894187971 on merged head 27187f3."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"hac-jwim"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Scheduled release candidate bump breaks hard-coded CLI version test"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Auto Release run 29894187971 correctly changed package.json and src/cli.ts from 2026.7.21-2 to the 2026.7.22 candidate, then release verification failed because tests/cli.test.ts asserted the old literal version."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":0},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["automation","github-actions","regression","release","testing","versioning"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/deadline","value":"2026-07-24T04:55:09.217Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/assignee","value":"codex-root"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-root"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":45},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"CLI composition verifies the Commander version against package.json rather than a stale literal; version.mjs check continues to enforce package.json and src/cli.ts parity; a dry-run candidate mutation proves the complete suite without publishing"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/definition_of_ready","value":"Exact run logs identify one deterministic assertion failure"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/goal","value":"Reliable conditional daily releases"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/objective","value":"Remove stale version literals from release verification"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/value","value":"Scheduled publication can complete after a date transition"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/impact","value":"Restores automatic release availability"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/outcome","value":"Candidate-aware version contract tests"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/why_now","value":"The first scheduled production run after the prior delivery failed"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"hac-suj3"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/reviewer","value":"unbraind"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":100},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/sprint","value":"api-contracts-2026-07-23"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/release","value":"2026.7.23"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/reporter","value":"github-actions"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/severity","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/environment","value":"GitHub-hosted ubuntu-24.04 scheduled Auto Release at merged master 27187f3"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/repro_steps","value":"Run node scripts/release/auto-release.mjs --push after a date transition with unreleased commits; release:verify fails in tests/cli.test.ts after version apply"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/expected_result","value":"Candidate version mutation passes tests because version parity is checked dynamically"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/actual_result","value":"Expected 2026.7.21-2 but received candidate 2026.7.22"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/affected_version","value":"2026.7.21-2"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/component","value":"release-automation"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/regression","value":true},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/customer_impact","value":"Daily releases are blocked and GitHub issue #65 remains open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"hac-5n71","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z","author":"codex-root"},{"id":"hac-l25p","kind":"discovered_from","created_at":"2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z","author":"codex-root"},{"id":"hac-m1kj","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z","author":"codex-root"},{"id":"hac-vooo","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z","author":"codex-root"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z","author":"codex-root","text":"This is distinct from hac-l25p: extension/tool provisioning passed; failure occurred after the candidate version was applied during the test gate."}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/notes","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z","author":"codex-root","text":"Keep dry-run and PR verification non-publishing; use temporary worktree or reversible apply evidence."}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/learnings","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z","author":"codex-root","text":"Release tests must assert invariants across candidate mutation,not literals from the previously published version."}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/files","value":[{"path":"tests/cli.test.ts","scope":"project","note":"Stale literal assertion"},{"path":"scripts/release/version.mjs","scope":"project","note":"Authoritative parity and candidate application logic"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tests","value":[{"command":"bunx vitest run tests/cli.test.ts","scope":"project","timeout_seconds":300}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/docs","value":[{"path":"docs/RELEASING.md","scope":"project","note":"Candidate verification model"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"bd69d5e34733a4b094b1ac9b89aa5c863f3fb2c1e97578f49b1602df97b549f4","message":"Create PM issue from exact hosted scheduled release failure"}
